7358,HTTP/2 requests do not follow redirects (maxRedirects ignored),2026-01-29 16:08:17+00:00,,open,1,['issue::bug'],"When httpVersion: 2 is used, Axios does not follow redirects, even with maxRedirects set. The HTTP/2 code path bypasses follow-redirects entirely, so redirect handling is skipped.

Evidence
https://github.com/axios/axios/blob/99d588dceaf20e8a2a2ab99c9188b4212f9f30b2/lib/adapters/http.js#L636-L652

Repro
```javascript
import axios from 'axios';

