4899,Content-Type header should be respected regardless of body,2022-08-01 05:59:15+00:00,2022-08-01 06:38:02+00:00,closed,1,[],"#### Describe the bug
#86 redux. I believe this behaviour to be incorrect. Here's an example of why: https://jsonapi.org/format/#content-negotiation-clients. Where it specifies:
```
