The work around would be to implement a whole new adapter which would be a great deal of work considering the very high number of config options handled "
3702,Can't completely remove User-Agent Header,2021-03-23 20:09:14+00:00,2021-03-29 14:47:30+00:00,closed,0,[],"#### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.
Some APIs only work if the User-Agent header is entirely omitted.  This is not currently possible in Axios in NodeJS.  #1411 opened this discussion some time back, but was closed without an actual solution other than commenting out the code which inserts the header.

