3506,Support AbortSignal for aborting requests,2020-12-29 22:35:36+00:00,2021-09-16 18:58:07+00:00,closed,2,[],"
#### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.

Node 15 has built-in support for `AbortController` and `AbortSignal` and request cancellation propagates all the way up to [`http.request`](https://nodejs.org/api/http.html#http_http_request_url_options_callback) taking a signal parameter.

