2168,Broken URL encoding,2019-05-23 09:43:32+00:00,2021-05-15 19:05:30+00:00,closed,3,[],"encode() function in lib/helpers/buildURL.js reverses percent-encoding done by encodeURIComponent in a way that explicitly breaks Spring backends which treat square bracket characters [ ] as delimiters.

