736,axios.delete - must specify 'data' object?,2017-03-03 05:00:00+00:00,2017-04-02 15:38:18+00:00,closed,22,[],"When using the alias `axios.delete`, the payload doesn't get sent with the API call if you don't specify `data`.

You have to do:
```javascript
axios.delete(URL, {
 data: { foo: 'bar' }
})
```
instead of 
```javascript
axios.delete(URL, { foo: 'bar' })
